

* how to go to expert mode
* mqtt topic prefix for in and out messages
* try various passwords for different modes, esp exp mode changes
* try and test changing configs - try with changes in radio, network, ap and mqtt configs
* heartbeat
* wdt reset

* test radio comm
* study radio message structure
* plan on ack and repeat ack messages,
* avoid sending mqtt messages for ack recd. 
* Is counter needed to deduplicate to avoid duplicate mqtt messages being generated due to duplicate radio messages
* work on topic and radio message structure and their remapping
* plan how the sensor nodes will be configured which are battery powered and shut down by itself. These may not have message counters.
